metadata.name: Premier Commercial Bancorp
metadata.description: As of July 2, 2018, Premier Commercial Bancorp was acquired by Heritage Financial Corporation. Premier Commercial Bancorp operates as the bank holding company for Premier Community Bank that provides banking services to businesses and individuals primarily in the state of Oregon. The company accepts various checking, savings, and money market accounts, as well as demand deposits and certificates of deposit. It also offers lending solutions consisting of term, commercial real estate, construction, and small business administration loans, as well as operating lines of credit. In addition, the company provides debit and credit cards; cash management services, such as e-statements, remote deposits, wire transfers, merchant services, fraud prevention, automated clearing house transactions, and automatic transfers; and online and mobile banking services. It operates through five full-service branches in Hillsboro, Forest Grove, Beaverton, Tigard, and Newberg of Oregon. The company was formerly known as Columbia Commercial Bancorp and changed its name to Premier Commercial Bancorp in April 2014. Premier Commercial Bancorp was founded in 1999 and is based in Hillsboro, Oregon.
